data.description: Check-out this amazing Harrsiville Mult-level!  NEW roof from 2018! Awesome location, near shopping and schools! Plenty of space in this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom with the main bathroom flooring updated, 2 living room home with another unfinished man cave/gym area or finished into another bedroom! An outstanding deck with big backyard that even has a garden and shade trees for the summer nights! RV parking and plenty of shelving in the garage for storage. This home is ready to have you call it home! Schedule your showing today!
